data.description:
MOTIVATED SELLERS!!! Come and check out this beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bath home located in Hope Mills. Just minutes away from shopping and dining, the location gives you a smaller town feel without being too far away from all the fun. But alas, fun can happen right in your backyard with an above ground pool AND hot tub. All of your new home dreams start right here... don't miss out.

Professional photos to come 11/16/2023
